---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'

import logo from '~/assets/partners/capgemini.png'
import location from '~/assets/location.jpg'

import Layout from '~/layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Layout>
  <div class="banner" style={{ backgroundImage: `url(${location.src})` }}>
    <p>
      <a href="https://www.capgemini.com" target="_blank" title="Capgemini">
        <button>Capgemini</button>
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="copy" id="two-column">
    <div class="column" id="biography">
      <h1>This is Capgemini</h1>

      <p>
        At Capgemini we work together on the newest software in an agile manner.
        Groundbreaking applications help our customers distinguish themselves
        from their competitors. These are complex projects, which we take on
        together. That is what we call "The Collaborative Business Experience":
        achieving good results by linking a team of experts from Capgemini to
        the client. This is how we create the best solutions with the newest
        technologies, allowing our clients to achieve maximal results.
      </p>

      <h1>The easy way</h1>

      <p>
        At Capgemini we like to make things easy for you, whether it concerns
        opportunities after graduating or nice internships. The most convenient
        option? Getting to know Capgemini through our XperienceDay. You sign up
        directly through
        <a
          href="https://www.experiencedays.nl"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">www.experiencedays.nl</a>.
          Want to apply for a job right away? Check out our job vacancies at
        <a
          href="https://www.werkenbijcapgemini.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">www.werkenbijcapgemini.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="column" id="photograph">
      <Image src={logo} alt="Capgemini logo" class="photograph" />
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
